### Test API endpoints

# Health Check
GET http://localhost:4000/health

###

# Authentication - Create Session (Magic Link)
POST http://localhost:4000/v1/auth/session
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com"
}

###

# Get Current User
GET http://localhost:4000/v1/me
Authorization: Bearer test-token

###

# Get Items (Browse Products)
GET http://localhost:4000/v1/items?category=office-chairs&condition=good&min_price=100&max_price=500

###

# Get Specific Item
GET http://localhost:4000/v1/items/650e8400-e29b-41d4-a716-446655440001

